text.tspan: A game by the Scralaxy Team, 2022 - 2024
- Added a working hammer in the overworld.
- Added credits page, listing all that have added updates.
- It is required to get the hammer if you want to use the hammer attack in battle.
- Added a button indicator for if you press z or x but not both on the titlescreen.
- Made the HAMMER variable reset each time, as it indicates if you have the hammer
- Added blocking in battle. If you block correctly, it will deal half damage.
- Made the jump actually look like you're jumping and not just posing.
- Added Conditional Battle Options in Battle//UI
